    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的示意图，用于健康科技团队培训。重点是让新人理解头部字段的分布，特别是Source Port到Data Offset这些核心字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Data Offset"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，TCP头部标准长度是20字节，但Options字段是可变的。您希望展示固定部分到哪个位置？还有，是否需要标注那些控制位，比如SYN、ACK、FIN这些？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options",
        "SYN",
        "ACK",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要完整展示。控制位部分从URG到FIN这6个标志位要单独标出来，每个占1位。另外Window字段16位，Checksum和Urgent Pointer也是16位。最后Options和Data部分我想标注成HealthTech_PatientRecords，强调这是我们实际传输的医疗数据负载。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "Options (HealthTech_PatientRecords)",
        "Data (HealthTech_PatientRecords)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了。我梳理一下：0-15位Source Port，16-31位Destination Port，32-63位Sequence Number，64-95位Acknowledgment Number。然后96-99位Data Offset，100-105位Reserved。106-111位依次是URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN。112-127位Window，128-143位Checksum，144-159位Urgent Pointer。160-191位Options，192-255位Data。两个可变部分都标注HealthTech_PatientRecords。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer",
        "Options (HealthTech_PatientRecords)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Reserved部分应该是6位，100-105没错。但确认一下Data Offset是4位对吧？还有Sequence Number和Acknowledgment Number都是32位，这个容易搞混。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Data Offset 4位（96-99），Sequence Number 32位（32-63），Acknowledgment Number 32位（64-95）。边界我都核对过了，没有重叠。现在可以开始绘制了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。标题用\"Estructura del paquete TCP\"，我们团队有拉美合作方，双语环境。另外Options和Data的标注要保持一致，都带HealthTech_PatientRecords后缀，突出这是患者记录数据的实际应用场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Options (HealthTech_PatientRecords)",
        "Data (HealthTech_PatientRecords)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
